Keto shepards pie : https://thebigmansworld.com/keto-shepherds-pie/#wprm-recipe-video-container-57027

= FOR THE FILLING
650g viande hachée 15% 1 tsp salt
    cook half quantity by half 
    in 10g duck fat each half

30g Tomato paste
2 cloves garlic minced
1 large onion chopped
100g peas
    optional
2 tsp moutarde
1 rib celery finely chopped
    optional
200g mushrooms finely chopped
 +  bit of olive oil to add flavor
    + use beef grease
    (no salt)

20g almond flour
12.5g fond de veau
    2g salt

1 tablespoon Worcestershire sauce
1 bay leaf
water

simmer for 1h


= FOR THE MASHED CAULIFLOWER : https://www.recipetineats.com/creamy-mashed-cauliflower/#wprm-recipe-container-36957
1 kg cauliflower florets surgelé
2 garlic cloves , peeled, whole
    add into boiling water and once water boils again cook for 15 minutes
    TEST if they're max softness !

30g butter
2 tsp dijon mustard
25g parmesan cheese , shredded
80g sour cream
a bit of cooking water
Pepper
1.5 tsp Salt


= FOR THE GOLDEN CRUST
sprinkle parmesan on top with hands
    cover everything

position grill
    
when out, sprinkle un peu de thym
